modified_SQL_query: SELECT TYPE_CONVERSION(INT) AS forcastid FROM QRM.Run_Time_Description WHERE AND(AND(AND(AND(AND(EQ(1, 1), EQ(Portfolio, @PortfolioCurrent)), EQ(TYPE_CONVERSION(Date), TYPE_CONVERSION(Date))), COMPARE(Strategy, @LikeMatchGap)), EQ(CompanyName, @CompanyName)), EQ(DateTimeStamp, (subquery_1)))

subquery_dictionary.subquery_1: SELECT MAX(DateTimeStamp) FROM QRM.Run_Time_Description WHERE AND(EQ(CompanyName, @CompanyName), EQ(Portfolio, @PortfolioCurrent))
